data.description: Welcome home! Beautiful Southgate ranch with plenty of updates! Newer vinyl thermal windows, newer asphalt roof, and newer vinyl siding; hardwood floors and custom molding throughout; newer ceiling fans in the living room and primary bedroom; living room with large picture window and cove ceilings that opens up to the eat-in kitchen with ceramic tile backsplash and plenty of cabinetry; bathroom in great condition with ceramic tile surround, walls, and flooring as well as a newer toilet and pedestal sink; full poured concrete basement with plenty of room for entertaining; doorwall leading to backyard brick paver patio; all just a few blocks away from both Grogan Elementary School and Cobb Memorial Park! Seller to provide Certificate of Occupancy at closing! Schedule a showing today!
